OL,3,CWeston dad runs 46 half marathons in
OL,4,C46 weeks in memory of son
OL,6,FA man from Weston is running 46 half
OL,7,Fmarathons in memory of his son.
OL,9,FTom Young's son Jaxon passed away on
OL,10,F14 May 2023 after 46 days on the
OL,11,Fneonatal intensive care unit at St
OL,12,FMichael's Hospital in Bristol.
OL,14,FDuring their time in hospital, Tom
OL,15,Fsaid he would chat to Jaxon about
OL,16,Frunning with him dressed as Superman.
