OL,3,CWeston dad runs 46 half marathons in
OL,4,C46 weeks in memory of son
OL,6,FSpeaking before the challenge started,
OL,7,FTom said: "I told Jaxon that when we
OL,8,Fwould leave the hospital, I would take
OL,9,Fhim along with me in his pushchair
OL,10,Fduring my next half marathon, dressed
OL,11,Fin my Superman suit.
OL,13,F"Knowing that I was sadly not able to
OL,14,Fdo this, my challenge is to run 46
OL,15,Fhalf marathons in 46 weeks dressed in
OL,16,Fa Superman suit, in memory of the 46
OL,17,Fdays we had with Jaxon."
OL,19,FOn 7 July 2023 Tom did the first half
OL,20,Fmarathon, and has been running nearly
OL,21,Fweekly since then.
