OL,3,CWeston dad runs 46 half marathons in
OL,4,C46 weeks in memory of son
OL,6,FTom said: "I wanted a massive
OL,7,Fchallenge to test myself and try and
OL,8,Fraise as much money as possible."
OL,10,FWhen he first started, Tom said he got
OL,11,Fa few confused looks from people, but
OL,12,Fnow he runs with a charity flag,
OL,13,Fpeople know what he's doing and have
OL,14,Ffollowed his journey on social media.
OL,16,FAt the time of writing, #6,000 has
OL,17,Fbeen raised for Cots for Tots - the
OL,18,Fcharity that worked alongside hospital
OL,19,Fstaff to care for Jaxon in his 46 days
OL,20,Fof life.
