OL,3,CWeston dad runs 46 half marathons in
OL,4,C46 weeks in memory of son
OL,6,FKate Jones, from Cots for Tots, said:
OL,7,F"Tom's fundraising will be helping
OL,8,Fhundreds of babies and families right
OL,9,Facross the South West.
OL,11,F"Channelling going through such a
OL,12,Fdifficult time by doing something so
OL,13,Fkind and amazing to help people
OL,14,Fthrough his fundraising is just really
OL,15,Finspiring and he's pretty amazing."
