OL,3,CWeston dad runs 46 half marathons in
OL,4,C46 weeks in memory of son
OL,6,FTom said: "(The challenge has) helped
OL,7,Fmassively. Before I go out I'll have a
OL,8,Fthink about him. Some days when I have
OL,9,Fa wobble where something really simple
OL,10,Fcan set me off, so I try and channel
OL,11,Fthat grief into my runs, I can use
OL,12,Fthat as a booster."
OL,14,FThe final run takes place on 14 May -
OL,15,Fon the first anniversary of Jaxon's
OL,16,Fdeath.
OL,18,FTom said: "I'm probably going to feel
OL,19,Fvery emotional, but I think I'll have
OL,20,Fso much adrenaline going through me it
OL,21,Fwill help massively, as a distraction."
